{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"1. It tried to read `step.Config[\"prompt\"]` directly as a file path, but the DSL parser stores the raw `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` string — not just the path. The fix adds `resolveStepConfigFile()` to extract the path from `file(\"...\")` syntax before reading.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T01:00:18.990943432Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"2. It didn't check `step.Config[\"run\"]` for script steps, so clicking a script step with `run = \"...\"` would show \"No content available\". The template also wasn't displaying `run` config keys.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T01:00:18.990953841Z"}
